channel.title: Problems with Starting my server up
channel.description:
Ok, well I just decided to get back into making servers and I just ( I Think) did everything i was supposed to do to start my server. I portforwarded (correctly), I mad a no-ip, I changed my firewall settings, and I redownloaded no-ip DUC. But none of this is working. I can get on my server without the ip but not with it.
Does any1 know what might be wrong.
